text: Adur Rouf Mia is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Gaibandha-2. ==Career== Mia was elected to parliament from Gaibandha-2 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Adur Rouf Mia
